Sentencas: Thermal expansion and conductivity measurements of LaCoO3-delta, EuCoO3-delta, Y1-xCoO3-delta and Y1-xCo1-yMnO3-delta Perovskites are presented and compared with magnetization and magnetic susceptibility data.
Titulo: High-temperature thermal expansion and conductivity of cobaltites: potentials for adaptation of the thermal expansion to the demands for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: An analysis by means of a phenomenological model reveals the importance of the spin state transition and its dependence on changes of the lattice structure in cobaltites.
Titulo: High-temperature thermal expansion and conductivity of cobaltites: potentials for adaptation of the thermal expansion to the demands for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The influence of the insulator-to-metal transition at high temperature on the thermal expansion is also discussed.
Titulo: High-temperature thermal expansion and conductivity of cobaltites: potentials for adaptation of the thermal expansion to the demands for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The potential of these compounds as cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) is evaluated.
Titulo: High-temperature thermal expansion and conductivity of cobaltites: potentials for adaptation of the thermal expansion to the demands for solid oxide fuel cells
